
@page "/prv"

<div class="container my-5 py-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
            
            <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5 bg-white">
                
                <div class="border-bottom pb-4 mb-4 text-center text-md-start">
                    <h1 class="fw-bold text-dark display-6 mb-2">Privacy Policy — Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA)</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-2"></i><em>Last Updated: May 2026</em>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-body text-secondary fs-6">
                    
                    <p class="lead text-dark mb-4">
                        Welcome to <strong>Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA)</strong>. Your privacy matters to us. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use our website and services.
                    </p>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                        <p>When using Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA), we may collect:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>URLs you paste into the analyzer</li>
                            <li>Basic browser/device information</li>
                            <li>Download history stored locally in your browser</li>
                            <li>Technical logs for security and performance monitoring</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect sensitive personal information unless you voluntarily provide it.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">2. How We Use Information</h2>
                        <p>We use collected information to:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>Analyze media links</li>
                            <li>Generate downloadable media previews</li>
                            <li>Improve site performance and user experience</li>
                            <li>Detect abuse, spam, or malicious activity</li>
                            <li>Maintain platform stability and security</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">3. Downloaded Content</h2>
                        <p>Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA) acts as a media analysis and download utility. Users are responsible for ensuring they have the legal right to download, use, or redistribute any content accessed through the platform. We do not claim ownership of third-party media.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">4. Cookies & Local Storage</h2>
                        <p>The site may use:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>Browser local storage</li>
                            <li>Session data</li>
                            <li>Essential cookies</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>These help:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>Remember interface preferences</li>
                            <li>Improve loading performance</li>
                            <li>Store temporary download history</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>We do not use invasive tracking technologies.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
                        <p>Some media content may originate from third-party platforms such as:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>TikTok</li>
                            <li>YouTube</li>
                            <li>Instagram</li>
                            <li>Twitter/X</li>
                            <li>Other public media providers</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Those platforms operate under their own privacy policies and terms.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
                        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect user information and maintain platform security. However, no online service can guarantee complete security. Use the service at your own discretion.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
                        <p>Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA) is not intended for children under 13 years old.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">8. Copyright & Responsibility</h2>
                        <p>Users are solely responsible for how downloaded media is used. You agree not to use the service for:</p>
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-3 custom-bullet-list">
                            <li>Copyright infringement</li>
                            <li>Unauthorized redistribution</li>
                            <li>Illegal content acquisition</li>
                            <li>Abuse of third-party platforms</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    <div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                        <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Continued use of the service after updates means you accept the revised policy.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4 opacity-25" />

                    @*<div class="policy-section mb-4">
                        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark h5 mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
                        <p>For questions or concerns regarding privacy or platform usage, contact:</p>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-light rounded-3 d-inline-block border">
                            <p class="mb-1 text-dark fw-bold">Vellum Media Analyzer(VMA) Support</p>
                            <a href="mailto:support@vellummedia.com" class="text-decoration-none text-primary fw-semibold">
                                <i class="bi bi-envelope-at me-2"></i>support@vellummedia.com
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div> *@

                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</div>